<br>
&quot;We were fighting the Gnolls in Qeynos Hills when a mighty gnoll runner, Gnasher Furgutt attacked us.  Piccolo soon became weak, but I kept him from dying, twice.  Unfortunately, *sniff* he was killed.&quot;<br>
<br>
